-59 South exit</li><li>Take the Greenbriar/Shepard exit</li><li>Turn right onto Greenbriar</li><li>Make a left onto College Ave. (Rice will be on your left)</li><li>Turn left onto Main Street</li><li>Gate 4 will be on your left.</li></ul></p>	</td>	<td class="w260 border-left padded right" valign="top" align="left">	<a href="index.php?c=about&p=history" class="tab">History</a> <a href="index.php?c=tour" class="tab">Tour</a> <a href="index.php?c=about&p=directions" class="tab">To Here</a> <a href="index.php?c=about&p=faqs" class="tab">FAQs</a>	<h1>Get Custom Directions</h1>	<h5>Use the following form to get custom directions to Hanszen.  Please input your starting address.</h5>	<form method="get" action="http://www.mapquest.com/directions/main.adp">		<input type="hidden" name="go" value="1">		<input type="hidden" name="do" value="nw">		<input type="hidden" name="rmm" value="1">		<input type="hidden" name="un" value="m">		<input type="hidden" name="cl" value="EN">		<input type="hidden" name="ct" value="NA">		<input type="hidden" name="rsres" value="1">		<input type="hidden" name="1y" value="US">		Address: <input type="text" name="1a"><br>		City: <input type="text" name="1c"><br>		State: <input type="text" name="1s" maxlength="2" size="2">		Zip-Code: <input type="text" name="1z" maxlength="5" size="5">		<input type="hidden" name="2y" value="US">		<input type="hidden" name="2a" value="6350 Main St">		<input type="hidden" name="2c" value="Houston">		<input type="hidden" name="2s" value="TX">		<input type="hidden" name="2z" value="77005">		<input type="submit" value="Get Directions!">	</form>	</td></tr></table></div><!-- Footer --><div id="footer">	<!-- Copyright Info -->Copyright &copy;2005 Hanszen Residential College, <a href="http://www.rice.edu/">Rice University</a>.  All rights reserved.</div></div></body></html>